{"tid":1800195,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［CelPay］加密貨幣PayMe式應用","createTime":"2019-12-27T14:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T09:12:24.000Z","uid":191531,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e16771651fc76065a3deda828305da18388cf26c","tid":1800195,"uid":191531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:37:05.000Z","msg":"CelPay，係Celsius Network個app入面嘅其中一個功能。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一句講晒，佢就係加密貨幣嘅PayMe，send條link / 喺app入面撳兩撳 就比倒錢人</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n+ 簡單<br />\n+ 無手續費<br />\n+ 英國公司（i.e. 非大陸/香港公司）<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n- 要KYC（i.e. 身份認證）<br />\n- 中心化<br />\n- 公司歷史短（2017創業）<br />\n<br />\n喺度講CelPay主要係貪佢簡化咗加密貨幣嘅比錢/收錢過程；個人認爲簡單化係<strong>打長遠經濟戰：快速普及化加密貨幣、減少依賴港幣</strong>嘅關鍵一環；Celsius Network嘅其他功能（e.g. 存款利息、法幣借貸）有興趣先再討論<br />\n<br />\n如果有高手識其他更好嘅applications請不吝賜教<br />\n<br />\n無推廣連結：<a href=\"https://celsius.network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcelsius.network%2F&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPFFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=cd7150ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://celsius.network/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df155d440d279be382ce403747d8921ff3e2a38d","tid":1800195,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都照推，順手借個位<br />\n（重要原則）想經濟攬炒，必須先紅後藍，否則只會事倍功半<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1799669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1799669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"676c6c8d75baa338d9309c61e8b7fe91dc666e68","tid":1800195,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:12:24.000Z","msg":"我們都有一個夢想<br />\n<br />\n穩固黃色經濟圈成型 新系統迎接新模式<br />\n<br />\n抵制支付寶來襲，抗衡八達通賣港<br />\n<br />\n屬於我地新時代既支付系統。<br />\n[招兵買馬] <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801706</a><br />\n[關注我們] <a href=\"https://t.me/TimesPayHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%